# Game Flow Diagram

## ROGUE NEURAL - Game State Flow

```mermaid
stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> Loading: Game Init

    Loading: Loading Screen
    Loading --> Scenario: Scenario Loaded

    Scenario: Scenario Display
    Scenario --> Playing: User Starts

    Playing: Active Gameplay
    Playing --> Ending_Choice: Choice Made
    Playing --> Playing: Phase Transition

    Ending_Choice: Processing Result
    Ending_Choice --> Ending_Calculation: Chaos Threshold Check

    Ending_Calculation: Calculate Ending
    Ending_Calculation --> GameEnd_Explosion: High Chaos
    Ending_Calculation --> GameEnd_Hackerman: Low Chaos
    Ending_Calculation --> GameEnd_Betrayal: Medium Chaos

    GameEnd_Explosion: Explosive Ending
    GameEnd_Hackerman: "Hackerman" Ending
    GameEnd_Betrayal: Betrayal Ending

    GameEnd_Explosion --> [*]
    GameEnd_Hackerman --> [*]
    GameEnd_Betrayal --> [*]

    Playing --> Reset: Reset Requested
    Scenario --> Reset: Reset Requested
```

