## ROGUE NEURAL - Component Architecture

```mermaid
classDiagram
    class Home {
        +useGameLogic()
        +renderChaosMeter()
        +renderScenarioDisplay()
        +renderGameInterface()
    }

    class useGameLogic {
        +gameState
        +scenario
        +phases
        +chaosLevel
        +logs
        +startGame()
        +handleChoice()
        +resetGame()
    }

    class ChaosMeter {
        +chaosLevel: number
        +renderMeter()
    }

    class ScenarioDisplay {
        +scenario: Scenario
        +onStartGame()
    }

    class GameInterface {
        +currentPhase: Phase
        +phases: Phase[]
        +logs: Log[]
        +choices: Choice[]
        +chaosLevel: number
        +onChoiceSelect()
    }

    class LogPanel {
        +logs: Log[]
        +renderLogs()
    }

    class ScenarioDisplay {
        +scenario: Scenario
        +renderScenario()
    }

    class ChoiceButton {
        +choice: Choice
        +onSelect()
    }

    Home --> useGameLogic : uses
    Home --> ChaosMeter : renders
    Home --> ScenarioDisplay : renders
    Home --> GameInterface : renders
    GameInterface --> LogPanel : renders
    GameInterface --> ScenarioDisplay : renders
    GameInterface --> ChoiceButton : renders multiple
```

