## ROGUE NEURAL - Data Model

```mermaid
classDiagram
    class Game {
        +GameId: string
        +State: GameState
        +ChaosLevel: number
        +CurrentPhaseIndex: number
    }

    class Scenario {
        +ScenarioId: string
        +Title: string
        +Description: string
        +Context: string
        +Entities: Entity[]
    }

    class Phase {
        +PhaseId: string
        +Title: string
        +Prompt: string
        +Choices: Choice[]
        +AIContext: AIContext
    }

    class Choice {
        +ChoiceId: string
        +Text: string
        +ChaosImpact: number
        +NarrativeImpact: NarrativeImpact
    }

    class Log {
        +LogId: string
        +Timestamp: Date
        +Type: LogType
        +Content: string
    }

    class Entity {
        +EntityId: string
        +Name: string
        +Role: string
        +Personality: string
        +InternalMonologue: Monologue[]
    }

    class Monologue {
        +Text: string
        +Tone: Tone
        +Context: string
    }

    Game "1" --> "1" Scenario : has
    Game "1" --> "1..*" Phase : contains
    Scenario "1" --> "1..*" Entity : contains
    Phase "1" --> "1..*" Choice : offers
    Game "1" --> "0..*" Log : generates
    Entity "1" --> "0..*" Monologue : thinks
```

