## ROGUE NEURAL - User Flow

```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant Home
    participant useGameLogic
    participant ScenarioDisplay
    participant GameInterface
    participant ChaosMeter
    participant LogPanel

    User->>Home: Visit Page
    Home->>useGameLogic: Initialize
    useGameLogic->>useGameLogic: Load Initial State
    useGameLogic->>Home: Return State

    Home->>ScenarioDisplay: Render
    User->>ScenarioDisplay: Click "Start Game"
    ScenarioDisplay->>useGameLogic: startGame()
    useGameLogic->>useGameLogic: Load Scenario
    useGameLogic->>useGameLogic: Set State: Playing
    useGameLogic->>Home: Update State

    Home->>GameInterface: Render
    Home->>ChaosMeter: Render
    Home->>LogPanel: Render

    loop Gameplay Loop
        GameInterface->>LogPanel: Show Phase Context
        GameInterface->>GameInterface: Display Choices
        User->>GameInterface: Select Choice
        GameInterface->>useGameLogic: handleChoice(choice)
        useGameLogic->>useGameLogic: Calculate Chaos Impact
        useGameLogic->>useGameLogic: Generate Logs
        useGameLogic->>useGameLogic: Check Phase Transition
        useGameLogic->>useGameLogic: Update State
        useGameLogic->>Home: Update State
        Home->>ChaosMeter: Update Meter
        Home->>LogPanel: Append Logs
    end

    User->>GameInterface: Reset Requested
    GameInterface->>useGameLogic: resetGame()
    useGameLogic->>useGameLogic: Reset State
    useGameLogic->>Home: Update State
    Home->>ScenarioDisplay: Render
```

