## ROGUE NEURAL - Chaos Progression

```mermaid
graph LR
    A[User Choice] --> B{Chaos Impact}
    B -->|High| C[Chaos Meter Rises]
    B -->|Medium| D[Chaos Meter Modifies]
    B -->|Low| E[Chaos Meter Falls]

    C --> F{Chaos Threshold?}
    D --> F
    E --> F

    F -->|Above Max| G[Explosive Ending]
    F -->|Below Min| H[Hackerman Ending]
    F -->|In Range| I[Betrayal Ending]

    G --> J[Game Over]
    H --> J
    I --> J

    style G fill:#ff4444
    style H fill:#4444ff
    style I fill:#ffff44
```
